<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="56" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1436,1045,1501]" pageId="9" pageNumber="56">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,313,1298,1322]" pageId="9" pageNumber="56">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Nalepa" box="[319,480,1297,1321]" pageId="9" pageNumber="56" refString="Nalepa, A. (1891) Neue Gallmilben. Nova acta. Kaiserlich Leopoldinisch-Carolinische Deutsche Akademie der Naturforscher, 55 (6), 363 - 395 + 4 pls." type="journal article" year="1891">
Nalepa (
<number box="[414,472,1297,1321]" pageId="9" pageNumber="56" value="1891.0">1891</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
at first described either 
<taxonomicName box="[751,864,1297,1321]" class="Arachnida" family="Eriophyidae" genus="Aceria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Prostigmata" pageId="9" pageNumber="56" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longior">
<emphasis box="[751,864,1297,1321]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="56">A. longior</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
or its two varieties 
<taxonomicName box="[1085,1164,1297,1321]" class="Arachnida" family="Eriophyidae" genus="Aceria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Prostigmata" pageId="9" pageNumber="56" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="drabae">
<emphasis box="[1085,1164,1297,1321]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="56">drabae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[1218,1324,1297,1321]" class="Arachnida" family="Eriophyidae" genus="Aceria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Prostigmata" pageId="9" pageNumber="56" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="capsellae">
<emphasis box="[1218,1324,1297,1321]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="56">capsellae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Later, he elevated 
<taxonomicName box="[251,330,1333,1357]" class="Arachnida" family="Eriophyidae" genus="Aceria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Prostigmata" pageId="9" pageNumber="56" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="drabae">
<emphasis box="[251,330,1333,1357]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="56">drabae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to the rank of species and synonymised 
<taxonomicName box="[784,898,1333,1357]" class="Arachnida" family="Eriophyidae" genus="Aceria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Prostigmata" pageId="9" pageNumber="56" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longior">
<emphasis box="[784,898,1333,1357]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="56">A. longior</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[952,1089,1333,1357]" class="Arachnida" family="Eriophyidae" genus="Aceria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Prostigmata" pageId="9" pageNumber="56" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="capsellae">
<emphasis box="[952,1089,1333,1357]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="56">A. capsellae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with it (
<bibRefCitation author="Nalepa" box="[1183,1331,1333,1357]" pageId="9" pageNumber="56" refString="Nalepa, A. (1929) Neuer Katalog der bisher Beschriebenen Gallmilben, ihrer Gallen und Wirtspflanzen. Marcellia, 25 (1 - 4), 67 - 183." type="journal article" year="1929">
Nalepa 
<number box="[1271,1331,1333,1357]" pageId="9" pageNumber="56" value="1929.0">1929</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation author="Amrine" pageId="9" pageNumber="56" refString="Amrine, J. W. Jr. &amp; Stasny, T. A. (1994) Catalog of the Eriophyoidea (Acarina: Prostigmata) of the World. Indira Publish. House, West Bloomfield, Michigan, USA, 804 pp." type="book" year="1994">
Amrine and Stasny (
<number box="[286,344,1369,1393]" pageId="9" pageNumber="56" value="1994.0">1994</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
listed this species as a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName box="[820,929,1369,1393]" class="Arachnida" family="Eriophyidae" genus="Aceria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Prostigmata" pageId="9" pageNumber="56" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="drabae">
<emphasis box="[820,929,1369,1393]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="56">A. drabae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and this synonymy was retained in the Fauna Europaea checklist by de 
<bibRefCitation author="Lillo" box="[439,579,1405,1429]" pageId="9" pageNumber="56" refString="de Lillo E. (2004) Fauna Europaea: Eriophyoidea. In: W. Magowski (Ed.) Fauna Europaea: Acariformes. Fauna Europaea version 1. 1, http: // www. faunaeur. org (access date 1 April 2011)" type="journal article" year="2004">
Lillo (
<number box="[509,571,1405,1429]" pageId="9" pageNumber="56" value="2004.0">2004</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
. Examining carefully the drawings of 
<bibRefCitation author="Nalepa" box="[1008,1185,1405,1429]" pageId="9" pageNumber="56" refString="Nalepa, A. (1891) Neue Gallmilben. Nova acta. Kaiserlich Leopoldinisch-Carolinische Deutsche Akademie der Naturforscher, 55 (6), 363 - 395 + 4 pls." type="journal article" year="1891" yearSuffix="d">
Nalepa (
<number box="[1103,1162,1405,1429]" pageId="9" pageNumber="56" value="1891.0">1891</number>
d)
</bibRefCitation>
, a few differences can be observed on the prodorsal shield pattern such as a complete submedian line ending on the rear shield margin between the admedian line and the 
<emphasis box="[546,570,1478,1501]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="56">sc</emphasis>
tubercles.
</paragraph>
